locations.description:
After all requirements are met, red lights will flash and an alarm will sound to signify the Safe Room is open.

**Single Use:** ✔

- Use [Object 11SR keycard (#11SR)](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/interchange?locationIds=28838) on the panel to open the Safe Room door

locations.title: Bunker Hermetic Door [All]
locations.description:
**Always Open:** ✔  
**Single Use:** ✘  
**Requirements:** Activate the [Hermetic Door Switch](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/reserve?locationIds=39277) (you then have 4 minutes to extract before needing to activate the switch again).  The light overhead must be green for extraction.

**Note:** Activating the lever has a chance to spawn Scav Raiders around the train station

locations.title: Armored Train [ALL]
locations.description:
Get inside the train before it departs.

**Always Open:** ✘  
**Single Use:** ✔  
**Requirements:** -

**Notes:** 
- Arrives between 25-35 minutes into the raid (20-10 minutes left)
- Stays for 7 minutes
- Honks twice on arrival
- Honks once 1 minute before departure
- Honks twice just before doors close

**Train Loot:**
- [Weapon Box [6x3]](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/reserve?locationIds=155270) - in the train carriage opposite the bunkers
- [Grenade Box](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/reserve?locationIds=155269) - in the train carriage opposite the bunkers, under a seat
- [Wooden Crate](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/reserve?locationIds=155268) - on top of some wooden boxes

locations.title: Raider Scav Mechanics
locations.description:
The Scav spawn mechanics on The Labs work differently to other maps.

Scav Raiders will begin spawning after 5 minutes.  Every couple of minutes there is a chance a Scav Raider will spawn. They can spawn anywhere and patrol anywhere.

Groups of 2-4 Scav Raiders will also spawn when any of the extraction buttons are pressed (you'll hear an announcement on the intercom).  When this happens, they spawn nearby the relevant extraction and patrol towards it.

locations.title: Sewage Conduit [PMC]

**Always Open:** ✔  
**Announcement:** None    
**Requirements:** Sink the water level using the [nearby control panel](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/lab?locationIds=31541). The water takes ~90 seconds to sink.

**Location:** Found in this [Duffle Bag](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/streets?locationIds=248184) in the maintenance room.

locations.title: Primorsky 46-48 Skybridge Key
locations.description:
**Unlocks:** [Primorsky 48 Apartment 10](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/streets?locationIds=249455)    
**Location:** On the shelf behind the bar counter. A single key is guaranteed to spawn every raid.

locations.title: Rusted Bloody Key
locations.description:
**Unlocks:** Unlocks the [door to the fourth floor of the Klimova 16A building](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/streets?locationIds=319087)  
**Location:** On the peg board behind the register in between the escalators. Two spawns on the pegboard. Top left corner and middle right side.  

**Note:** Has a 5% spawn chance at this location.  Can also be found at random in Jackets/Drawers/Scavs

locations.title: Relaxation room key
locations.description:
**Unlocks:** [The Hive](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/streets?locationIds=316292)  

100% chance to spawn in the [IT Building](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/streets?locationIds=316406) every round.  There are 12 possible spawn locations throughout the building.  Can also be found at random from Jackets/Drawers/Scavs

locations.title: "Negotiation" room key

- Snipers will fire if extraction zone is entered before firing flare

locations.title: BTR Rodina Cinema
locations.description:
The BTR is a taxi service in Streets of Tarkov.  It will take you to another BTR location for a price that changes based on if you are a Scav or a PMC.  Expect to pay as much as 10,000 rubles for each trip.  You have about 2 minutes to book your trip with the BTR driver, else you'll be automatically removed from the vehicle.   

Also via the BTR, PMCs may move items, that fit in a 2x4 container, from the raid to their stash for a fee that varies based on the value of the items.

All BTR locations:
- [BTR Rodina Cinema](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/streets?locationIds=317348)
- [BTR Pinewood Hotel](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/streets?locationIds=317349)
- [BTR Tram](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/streets?locationIds=317350)
- [BTR City Center](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/streets?locationIds=317351)
- [BTR Collapsed Crane](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/streets?locationIds=317352)
- [BTR Scav Checkpoint](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/streets?locationIds=317353)

locations.title: Stash a beanie and sunglasses in the barber shop [Dandies]
locations.description:
**Quest:** Dandies  
**Quest Giver:** Ragman  
**Requirements:** Bomber beanie, RayBench Hipster Reserve sunglasses

**Task:**
- Kill 30 enemies of any type while wearing the beanie and sunglasses.  
- Head to the [Barber Shop](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/streets?locationIds=317484) to stash the items.
- First stash location is on the round coffee table to the right immediately after entering the shop from the south.  
- Second stash location is in between the two barber chairs to the left after entering the shop from the south.

**Behind the Lock:** 
- [Scientist's Hard Drive](https://mapgenie.io/tarkov/maps/ground-zero?locationIds=314922)
- Multiple PC Blocks
- Four filing cabinets
- Duffle Bag (next to the left PC under the wall opposite from windows, doesn't always spawn)

**Note:** You do not need the key to enter this room. You can enter it through the windows, using the wide windowsill from the next room.
